lead_paragraph: Lou Williams scored a season-high 30 points, and the Los Angeles Lakers sent Phoenix to its ninth straight loss with a 97-77 rout of the cold-shooting Suns on Sunday night.

headline.print_headline: Williams Scores 30, Lakers Beat Suns 97-77 Without Kobe
